{{ja-kanjitab|かばね|yomi=k}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|sort=かばね|-}}.  Found in the ''{{w|Man'yōshū}}'', completed some time after 759 CE.<ref>{{RQ:Manyoshu|18|4094}}, text [http://jti.lib.virginia.edu/japanese/manyoshu/Man18Yo.html#4094 here]</ref>

Appears to be a compound.  Ultimate derivation {{unk|ja|sort=かばね|nocap=1}}.

{{ja-noun|しかばね}}

